verbose_text: Therefore, we apply the same corrections to both OMI and TROPOMI level 3 data as follows : corrected OMI TropNO 2 VCDs in LNY of year yi are defined as (2) corr.OMIyiij =O MIyiij-0.5xcij, and corrected TROPOMI TropNO 2 VCDs are defined as (3) corr.TROPOMIyiij = TROPOMIyi +0.5 xcij, A map of the correction term c (i, j) is shown in the panel (j) of XREF_FIG.
